Gather smarter feedback from Day One.

Dex is the adaptive layer for self-improving feedback systems that scale with your business. Imagine a 24/7 team of digital researchers embedded across every touchpointsegmenting users, analyzing insights, and optimizing research around the clockall while delivering a tailored user experience. Were reimagining surveys through a dev-first approach.

Building Dexterity (W25). Prev Math at Harvard, Jump Trading, Meta, IBM.

Dexterity
 

Regina Lin, Founder/CEO

Regina is the Co-Founder & CEO of Dexterity. She dropped out of Harvard, where she studied Mathematics with a concurrent master's in Computational Science. She previously co-founded Contour AI, a devOps tool for LLM evaluation, and helped build the first MVP of Bazar, a GC-backed ecommerce marketplace with 40K+ customers. She previously held various investment analysis roles across public & private financial markets, and founded a nonprofit in Dallas with 300+ volunteers.
Regina Lin
Dexterity
